_aChangeLog.text: New intro room that presents the whole map as a mini-map
Blue among us character skin giver when you complete 02 climb.
Wall on the race to help prevent people skipping the last segment
A hurter under disco. (Both teams can be hurt by it)
A secret nod to a helpful person.
Added a ladder in the vent below cell-vent.
Table issue staying red in cell area has been fixed.
Starting rounds with friendly fire due to traitor has been fixed.
Changed straw game bottom texture to something more fitting.

_sText:
>New update, just redownload the file provided.<

Jb among us took about 3 weeks to make. A fun little project I worked on. A few people joked about the idea of making an among us x Jailbreak map, I joked about it too till I played around with making textures and thought "sod it".

 All custom textures aside a few.
Custom textures are made by myself, though I will be posting a texture pack shortly.
